{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/projects/imperial-russia","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>Imerial Russia</strong> is a historic unit converter app for Android. It also includes simple arithmetic calculator. Written in Kotlin. Minimum supported Android version is 4.4.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:2.0375;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.079754601226995%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Russian landscape\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/a6d36/imperial-russia-feature.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/222b7/imperial-russia-feature.png 163w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/ff46a/imperial-russia-feature.png 325w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/a6d36/imperial-russia-feature.png 650w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/e548f/imperial-russia-feature.png 975w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/3c492/imperial-russia-feature.png 1300w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/29114/imperial-russia-feature.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"roadmap\" style=\"position:relative;\">Roadmap<a href=\"#roadmap\" aria-label=\"roadmap permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Another unit types: volume, weight</li>\n<li>Slavic calendar</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"download\" style=\"position:relative;\">Download<a href=\"#download\" aria-label=\"download permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.github.mikolasan.imperialrussia\">\n<img alt=\"Get it on Google Play\" src=\"https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png\" height=\"80\">\n</a>\n<h2 id=\"about\" style=\"position:relative;\">About<a href=\"#about\" aria-label=\"about permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>If you are reading a literary book about 18th century, or studying history, or you feel limited with the standard units of measurements, or by any other means find yourself curious about historic units used one or two centuries ago, like when it was time of Russian Empire, then this app might take you interest.</p>\n<p>Jump into the new world measured by arshin, versta, sazhen. Measure like Russian.</p>\n<h2 id=\"privacy-policy\" style=\"position:relative;\">Privacy policy<a href=\"#privacy-policy\" aria-label=\"privacy policy permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"https://neupokoev.xyz/projects/imperial-russia/privacy-policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this privacy policy</a> for details.</p>\n<h2 id=\"for-developers\" style=\"position:relative;\">For developers<a href=\"#for-developers\" aria-label=\"for developers permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"architecture\" style=\"position:relative;\">Architecture<a href=\"#architecture\" aria-label=\"architecture permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Kotlin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://square.github.io/kotlinpoet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">KotlinPoet</a> for genereting complete graph of conversions</li>\n<li>ViewPager</li>\n<li>RecyclerView</li>\n<li>Simple <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recursive_descent_parser\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">recursive descent parser</a> in the calculator</li>\n<li>SharedPreferences for persistancy</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://noties.io/Markwon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Markwon</a> Markdown library without WebView requirement</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observer_pattern\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Observer pattern</a> used in the Main Activity. Child fragments call method in the activity and depending on the layout if other fragments exist, then the message will be delivered to them.</li>\n<li>Different layouts: landscape (no main panels), tablet landscape (additional info panel), portrait, spacious portrait (additional info panel). Smart watch and auto layouts are in the roadmap.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"next\" style=\"position:relative;\">Next<a href=\"#next\" aria-label=\"next permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Apply <a href=\"https://jakewharton.com/shrinking-a-kotlin-binary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this tutorial</a> to reduce the app size.</p>","excerpt":"Imerial Russia is a historic unit converter app for Android. It also includes simple arithmetic calculator. Written in Kotlin. Minimum…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#roadmap\">Roadmap</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#download\">Download</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#about\">About</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#privacy-policy\">Privacy policy</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#for-developers\">For developers</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#architecture\">Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#next\">Next</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/67a41333-a021-50bc-ba68-c426305dbded.jpg"},"frontma